<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,370,1053,1080]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="14">Grallaria saturata</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Domaniewski, J. &amp; Stolzmann, J." box="[378,795,1053,1079]" pageId="13" pageNumber="14" pagination="479 - 484" refId="ref21909" refString="Domaniewski, J. &amp; Stolzmann, J. (1918) Contribution a la connaissance des formes du genre Grallaria Vieillot. In: Comptes rendus des seances: Classe 4, Sciences biologiques. Societe scientifique de Varsowie, Varsowie, pp. 479 - 484." type="book chapter" year="1918">Domaniewski &amp; Stolzmann, 1918</bibRefCitation>
